Privacy Policy

[KARMA] ("the Bot") is provided by [Aryyan24] ("the Developer"). This Privacy Policy explains how information about you is collected, used, and disclosed by the Bot.

Information Collection and Use

The Bot does not collect any personal information from users. However, certain non-personal information may be collected automatically, including but not limited to:

Usage data: Information about your interactions with the Bot, such as commands executed, messages sent, and settings adjusted.
Device information: Information about your device, such as device type, operating system, and IP address.
Use of Information

The information collected by the Bot is used solely for the purpose of providing and improving the Bot's functionality. This may include:

Analyzing usage patterns to optimize performance and user experience.
Debugging and troubleshooting technical issues.
Enforcing compliance with applicable terms and conditions.
Information Sharing and Disclosure

The Bot does not share any information collected from users with third parties, except as required by law or to protect the rights, property, or safety of the Developer or others.

Security

The Developer takes reasonable measures to protect the information collected by the Bot from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.

Children's Privacy

The Bot is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. The Developer does not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe that your child has provided personal information to the Bot, please contact the Developer to have it removed.

Changes to this Privacy Policy

The Developer reserves the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting. Your continued use of the Bot after any such changes constitutes acceptance of the revised Privacy Policy.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact the Developer at [discord - aryyan24].

